  <scopecontent id="aspace_8f0623c3c2ba77c3b5dd28b7607d2cea">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Records of the Reformed Church of Interlaken, New York, a Dutch Reformed church (formerly the Reformed Dutch Church of Farmerville, New York), including minutes, membership lists, and records of baptisms and marriages.</p>  </scopecontent>
